    🔹 CORE TECHNOLOGY
    Discord Server Booster operates by generating and managing virtual accounts that can boost Discord servers. The program uses advanced token generation algorithms combined with proxy rotation to create legitimate-looking accounts that can be used for server boosting. These accounts are then automatically configured to apply their boosts to your specified server, increasing its boost count and unlocking higher-tier perks .
    
    🔹 BOOSTING PROCESS
    The software follows a sophisticated multi-step process:
    
    • TOKEN GENERATION: Creates unique Discord authentication tokens using advanced algorithms
    • PROXY INTEGRATION: Routes each booster through different proxies to avoid detection
    • ACCOUNT SETUP: Automatically configures accounts with randomized usernames and avatars
    • BOOST APPLICATION: Joins your server and applies Nitro boosts
    • MAINTENANCE: Keeps boosters active and reapplies boosts if they expire
    
